 1958, NASA succeeded the National Advisory Committee for Aeronautics (NACA) to give the American space development effort a distinct civilian orientation, emphasizing peaceful applications in space science. It has since led most of America’s space exploration programs, including Project Mercury, Project Gemini, the 1968–1972 Apollo program missions, the Skylab space station, and the Space Shuttle.\n.\n.", "duration": 5.033, "timestamp": 1775249217, "uploader_id": "7116785092", "uploader": "المبرمج م/اسامة فاضل | Osamh Fadel", "channel": "lky_112l", "like_count": 13687, "comment_count": 89, "comments": [{"author": "ciaosonowolf3212", "author_id": "30854150859", "id": "18103013131973492", "text": "", "timestamp": 1778233083}, {"author": "adam9270407", "author_id": "77739811920", "id": "17947365615174182", "text": "Thanks", "timestamp": 1777740898}, {"author": "michael9821502", "author_id": "78266881138", "id": "18006259346899642", "text": "Did you type: 1-30  or how did you get the content:) ?\nAnyway truly apppreciated, sincerely!!!", "timestamp": 1777728594}, {"author": "abaya_majhi", "author_id": "34983480155", "id": "18580966804058721", "text": "Nic information", "timestamp": 1777038186}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://instagram.ftlv5-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/657861030_18352358068233093_7324284146102156944_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi41NDAuc2RyLnZpZGVvX2RlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=instagram.ftlv5-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=109&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEmLO4Qx3Va_WeHRNpDXP6FwmEJuDNGslDbtKrSfinhvXrr62eHV8Qm2DZekU_mzImHPmq_EY8EChcFKEAGFHdC&_nc_ohc=GOGtaSgv3HcQ7kNvwEDwIcE&_nc_gid=DUvr0t_h2lTZUUfpFCKnaQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af6x58TbtC3Ae7I4rx1DWpOV6pxt92WNJgMFxG2H1JzuOA&oe=6A111095&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1137, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1137"}, {"url": "https://instagram.ftlv5-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/657861030_18352358068233093_7324284146102156944_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb